#. +> trunk5
#: ../../user_manual/getting_started.rst:5
msgid "Getting Started"
msgstr "はじめに"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../user_manual/getting_started.rst:7
msgid ""
"Welcome to the Krita Manual! In this section, we'll try to get you up to "
"speed."
msgstr ""
"Krita マニュアルへようこそ! このセクションでは初心者の方に情報を提供します。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../user_manual/getting_started.rst:9
msgid ""
"If you are familiar with digital painting, we recommend checking out "
"the :ref:`introduction_from_other_software` category, which contains guides "
"that will help you get familiar with Krita by comparing its functions to "
"other software."
msgstr ""
"もしあなたがデジタルお絵描きに慣れているな"
"ら、:ref:`introduction_from_other_software` カテゴリを参照することをお勧めし"
"ます。Krita が他のソフトとどのような機能の違いがあるのかのガイドがあります。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../user_manual/getting_started.rst:11
msgid ""
"If you are new to digital art, just start with :ref:`installation`, which "
"deals with installing Krita, and continue on to :ref:`starting_with_krita`, "
"which helps with making a new document and saving it, :ref:`basic_concepts`, "
"in which we'll try to quickly cover the big categories of Krita's "
"functionality, and finally, :ref:`navigation`, which helps you find basic "
"usage help, such as panning, zooming and rotating."
msgstr ""
"もしデジタルアートは初めてなら、:ref:`installation` から始めましょう。Krita "
"をインストールすることから始め、:ref:`starting_with_krita` に進みドキュメント"
"を新しく作ったり保存し、:ref:`basic_concepts` で Krita の大まかの機能の簡単な"
"説明を、最後に :ref:`navigation` でパン、ズーム、回転といったヘルプツールにつ"
"いて学べます。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../user_manual/getting_started.rst:13
msgid ""
"When you have mastered those, you can look into the dedicated introduction "
"pages for functionality in the :ref:`user_manual`, read through the "
"overarching concepts behind (digital) painting in "
"the :ref:`general_concepts` section, or just search "
"the :ref:`reference_manual` for what a specific button does."
msgstr ""
"それらをマスターしたら、:ref:`user_manual` にある機能の紹介ページに行った"
"り、:ref:`general_concepts` のところで(デジタル)アートの背後にある包括的な概"
"念を読み通したり、または :ref:`reference_manual` でどのボタンが何をするか探し"
"て見ると良いでしょう。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../user_manual/getting_started.rst:15
msgid "Contents:"
msgstr "コンテンツ:"
